metadata.name: #001 - WOT - Pink
metadata.description:
Alecia Beth Moore (born September 8, 1979), known professionally as P!nk, is an American singer and songwriter. 

In 2007 P!nk was featured for the first time at the Billboard Top Artists - Female list, in the 9th place, which makes her a Women on Top!

Every piece in this collection was hand drawn by me, using the exclusive Phone & Fingers Photorealism techinque.
